SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct(st.st_id), st.st_omschrijving from kw_status st, kw_statusflow_verwerking stf where stf.stf_aanvraagtype_id = ~1 and (st.st_id = stf.stf_status_oud or st.st_id = stf.stf_status_nieuw) and not exists (select mpss.mprs_st_id, mp.mapr_id, mp.mapr_avt_id from kw_main_process_status mpss, kw_main_processes mp where mp.mapr_avt_id = ~1 and mp.mapr_id=mpss.mprs_mapr_id and mpss.mprs_st_id = st.st_id and mp.mapr_avt_volgnummer = ~2 ) order by st.st_id
